				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-444510/ground-control#post-4346275</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2019 02:01:51 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Bassoe</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3070028</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Theory: the Presence is another <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/stealingsolidarityhub">baby Overseer</a>. We already have <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-2085">one bloke with a spacesuit and larval eldritch abomination hanging around in his chest cavity</a>, possibly we've got something going around snatching and <a href="https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FaceFullOfAlienWingWong">impregnating</a> astronauts. Difference is, Simon got back to earth and was rescued by a bunch of cyborg catgirls while SCP-1959 is still stuck in orbit.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
