					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-444510#post-4133352</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-444510/ground-control#post-4133352</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 28 Jan 2019 09:51:55 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Monteparnas</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2926286</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It seems like his equipment is still picking up radio signals, so he's mostly aware of Earth's transmissions. And given his low orbit, he's still picking up satellite transmissions today. So he can be reasonably well informed on current developments, and does have something, if little, to distracting him and also to remember the people he is protecting.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
